      <h1>About BodyMorph</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>BodyMorph</strong>, a customizable fitness app designed to help you achieve your fitness goals. 
        Whether you're an athlete, a fitness enthusiast, or just starting your journey, BodyMorph is here to guide you 
        with personalized workout plans tailored to your body type, fitness preferences, and goals.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes BodyMorph Unique?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personalized Plans:</strong> Tailored workouts based on your height, weight, body type, and goals.</li>
        <li><strong>Dynamic Grouping:</strong> Organize your saved exercises into categories for better planning.</li>
        <li><strong>Ease of Use:</strong> Simple and intuitive interface for managing your fitness journey.</li>
        <li><strong>Customization:</strong> Update your profile as your goals and progress evolve.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At BodyMorph, we believe that fitness is not a one-size-fits-all solution. Our mission is to empower individuals 
        to unlock their full potential by offering tools and technology that adapt to their unique needs. 
        Fitness is a journey, and we're here to help you every step of the way.
      </p>

      <h2>Future Vision</h2>
      <p>
        We're continually evolving to bring new features to BodyMorph, including wearable device integration, 
        AI-driven workout recommendations, and progress tracking tools. Stay tuned as we work to make your fitness journey 
        even more effective and enjoyable!
